        COMMAND ninja audio_decoder_g711
        )


set(audio_encoder_g711_sources
        ${EMPTY_PATH}
        ${webrtc_source_path}api/audio_codecs/g711/audio_encoder_g711.cc
        ${webrtc_source_path}api/audio_codecs/g711/audio_encoder_g711.h
        )

        ${audio_encoder_g711_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(audio_encoder_g711 PRIVATE
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        WEBRTC_ENABLE_PROTOBUF=1
        WEBRTC_INCLUDE_INTERNAL_AUDIO_DEVICE
        RTC_ENABLE_VP9
        RTC_DAV1D_IN_INTERNAL_DECODER_FACTORY
        WEBRTC_HAVE_SCTP
        WEBRTC_USE_H264
        WEBRTC_ARCH_ARM64
        WEBRTC_HAS_NEON
        WEBRTC_LIBRARY_IMPL
        WEBRTC_ENABLE_AVX2
        WEBRTC_NON_STATIC_TRACE_EVENT_HANDLERS=0
        WEBRTC_POSIX
        WEBRTC_LINUX
        WEBRTC_ANDROID
        ABSL_ALLOCATOR_NOTHROW=1
        )

target_include_directories(audio_encoder_g711 PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/abseil-cpp/
        )

        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja audio_encoder_g711
        )

        PA_PCSCAN_STACK_SUPPORTED
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        BASE_IMPLEMENTATION
        U_USING_ICU_NAMESPACE=0
        U_ENABLE_DYLOAD=0
        USE_CHROMIUM_ICU=1
        U_ENABLE_TRACING=1
        U_ENABLE_RESOURCE_TRACING=0
        U_STATIC_IMPLEMENTATION
        ICU_UTIL_DATA_IMPL=ICU_UTIL_DATA_FILE
        )

target_include_directories(base PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/abseil-cpp/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/boringssl/src/include/

        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/icu/source/common/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/icu/source/i18n/
        )

        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja base
        )

        ${webrtc_source_path}examples/unityplugin/simple_peer_connection.cc
        ${webrtc_source_path}examples/unityplugin/simple_peer_connection.h
        ${webrtc_source_path}examples/unityplugin/unity_plugin_apis.cc
        ${webrtc_source_path}examples/unityplugin/unity_plugin_apis.h
        ${webrtc_source_path}examples/unityplugin/video_observer.cc
        ${webrtc_source_path}examples/unityplugin/video_observer.h
        ${webrtc_source_path}examples/unityplugin/class_reference_holder.cc
        ${webrtc_source_path}examples/unityplugin/class_reference_holder.h
        ${webrtc_source_path}examples/unityplugin/jni_onload.cc
        )

add_library(webrtc_unity_plugin_static STATIC
        ${webrtc_unity_plugin_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(webrtc_unity_plugin_static PRIVATE
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        WEBRTC_ENABLE_PROTOBUF=1
        WEBRTC_INCLUDE_INTERNAL_AUDIO_DEVICE
        RTC_ENABLE_VP9
        RTC_DAV1D_IN_INTERNAL_DECODER_FACTORY
        WEBRTC_HAVE_SCTP
        WEBRTC_USE_H264
        WEBRTC_ARCH_ARM64
        WEBRTC_HAS_NEON
        WEBRTC_ENABLE_AVX2
        WEBRTC_NON_STATIC_TRACE_EVENT_HANDLERS=0
        WEBRTC_POSIX
        WEBRTC_LINUX
        WEBRTC_ANDROID
        ABSL_ALLOCATOR_NOTHROW=1
        ABSL_FLAGS_STRIP_NAMES=0
        HAVE_WEBRTC_VIDEO
        )

target_include_directories(webrtc_unity_plugin_static PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/abseil-cpp/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/libyuv/include/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET webrtc_unity_plugin_static PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja webrtc_unity_plugin
        )

add_library(webrtc_unity_plugin SHARED
        ${EMPTY_PATH}
        )

        RTC_ENABLE_VP9
        RTC_DAV1D_IN_INTERNAL_DECODER_FACTORY
        WEBRTC_HAVE_SCTP
        WEBRTC_USE_H264
        WEBRTC_ARCH_ARM64
        WEBRTC_HAS_NEON
        WEBRTC_LIBRARY_IMPL
        WEBRTC_ENABLE_AVX2
        WEBRTC_NON_STATIC_TRACE_EVENT_HANDLERS=0
        WEBRTC_POSIX
        WEBRTC_LINUX
        WEBRTC_ANDROID
        ABSL_ALLOCATOR_NOTHROW=1
        )

        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/abseil-cpp/
        )

        )

        ${webrtc_source_path}test/time_controller/external_time_controller.cc
        ${webrtc_source_path}test/time_controller/external_time_controller.h
        ${webrtc_source_path}test/time_controller/real_time_controller.cc
        ${webrtc_source_path}test/time_controller/real_time_controller.h
        ${webrtc_source_path}test/time_controller/simulated_process_thread.cc
        ${webrtc_source_path}test/time_controller/simulated_process_thread.h
        ${webrtc_source_path}test/time_controller/simulated_task_queue.cc
        ${webrtc_source_path}test/time_controller/simulated_task_queue.h
        ${webrtc_source_path}test/time_controller/simulated_thread.cc
        ${webrtc_source_path}test/time_controller/simulated_thread.h
        ${webrtc_source_path}test/time_controller/simulated_time_controller.cc
        ${webrtc_source_path}test/time_controller/simulated_time_controller.h
        )

add_library(time_controller8 STATIC
        ${time_controller8_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(time_controller8 PRIVATE
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        WEBRTC_ENABLE_PROTOBUF=1
        WEBRTC_INCLUDE_INTERNAL_AUDIO_DEVICE
        RTC_ENABLE_VP9
        RTC_DAV1D_IN_INTERNAL_DECODER_FACTORY
        WEBRTC_HAVE_SCTP
        WEBRTC_USE_H264
        WEBRTC_ARCH_ARM64
        WEBRTC_HAS_NEON
        WEBRTC_LIBRARY_IMPL
        WEBRTC_ENABLE_AVX2
        WEBRTC_NON_STATIC_TRACE_EVENT_HANDLERS=0
        WEBRTC_POSIX
        WEBRTC_LINUX
        WEBRTC_ANDROID
        ABSL_ALLOCATOR_NOTHROW=1
        ABSL_FLAGS_STRIP_NAMES=0
        )

target_include_directories(time_controller8 PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/abseil-cpp/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET time_controller8 PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja time_controller8
        )

        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        )

target_include_directories(fiat_license PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET fiat_license PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja fiat_license
        )

        BORINGSSL_ALLOW_CXX_RUNTIME
        BORINGSSL_NO_STATIC_INITIALIZER
        OPENSSL_SMALL
        _XOPEN_SOURCE=700
        )

        )

        COMMAND ninja boringssl
        )

        ${ffmpeg_internal_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(ffmpeg_internal PRIVATE
        HAVE_AV_CONFIG_H
        _POSIX_C_SOURCE=200112
        _XOPEN_SOURCE=600
        PIC
        FFMPEG_CONFIGURATION=NULL
        _ISOC99_SOURCE
        _LARGEFILE_SOURCE
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        OPUS_FIXED_POINT
        )

target_include_directories(ffmpeg_internal PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/ffmpeg/chromium/config/Chrome/android/arm64/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/ffmpeg/
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/opus/src/include/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET ffmpeg_internal PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja ffmpeg_internal
        )

  ${google_benchmark_sources}
)

target_compile_definitions(google_benchmark PRIVATE
  HAVE_GNU_POSIX_REGEX=0
  HAVE_POSIX_REGEX=0
  HAVE_STD_REGEX=1
  _GNU_SOURCE
  ANDROID
  HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
  ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
  _DEBUG
  DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
)

target_include_directories(google_benchmark PRIVATE
  ${webrtc_source_path}
  ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
  ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/google_benchmark/src/include/
)

add_custom_command(TARGET google_benchmark PRE_BUILD
  WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
  COMMAND ninja google_benchmark
)
]]

set(hb_scoped_util_sources
        ${EMPTY_PATH}
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/harfbuzz-ng/utils/hb_scoped.h
        )

add_library(hb_scoped_util STATIC
        ${hb_scoped_util_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(hb_scoped_util PRIVATE
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        FT_CONFIG_MODULES_H="freetype-custom/freetype/config/ftmodule.h"
        FT_CONFIG_OPTIONS_H="freetype-custom/freetype/config/ftoption.h"
        WITHOUT_HARFBUZZ
        CHROMIUM_RESTRICT_VISIBILITY
        )

target_include_directories(hb_scoped_util PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/freetype/include/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/freetype/include/freetype-custom/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/freetype/src/include/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/harfbuzz-ng/src/src/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET hb_scoped_util PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja hb_scoped_util
        )

add_library(icui18n STATIC
        ${icui18n_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(icui18n PRIVATE
        U_I18N_IMPLEMENTATION
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        HAVE_DLOPEN=0
        UCONFIG_ONLY_HTML_CONVERSION=1
        UCONFIG_USE_WINDOWS_LCID_MAPPING_API=0
        U_CHARSET_IS_UTF8=1
        U_USING_ICU_NAMESPACE=0
        U_ENABLE_DYLOAD=0
        USE_CHROMIUM_ICU=1
        U_ENABLE_TRACING=1
        U_ENABLE_RESOURCE_TRACING=0
        U_STATIC_IMPLEMENTATION
        ICU_UTIL_DATA_IMPL=ICU_UTIL_DATA_FILE
        )

target_include_directories(icui18n PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/icu/source/common/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/icu/source/i18n/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET icui18n PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja icui18n
        )

add_library(icui18n_hidden_visibility STATIC
        ${icui18n_hidden_visibility_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(icui18n_hidden_visibility PRIVATE
        U_I18N_IMPLEMENTATION
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        HAVE_DLOPEN=0
        UCONFIG_ONLY_HTML_CONVERSION=1
        UCONFIG_USE_WINDOWS_LCID_MAPPING_API=0
        U_CHARSET_IS_UTF8=1
        U_USING_ICU_NAMESPACE=0
        U_ENABLE_DYLOAD=0
        USE_CHROMIUM_ICU=1
        U_ENABLE_TRACING=1
        U_ENABLE_RESOURCE_TRACING=0
        U_STATIC_IMPLEMENTATION
        ICU_UTIL_DATA_IMPL=ICU_UTIL_DATA_FILE
        )

target_include_directories(icui18n_hidden_visibility PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/icu/source/common/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/icu/source/i18n/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET icui18n_hidden_visibility PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja icui18n_hidden_visibility
        )

add_library(icuuc_private STATIC
        ${icuuc_private_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(icuuc_private PRIVATE
        U_COMMON_IMPLEMENTATION
        U_ICUDATAENTRY_IN_COMMON
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        HAVE_DLOPEN=0
        UCONFIG_ONLY_HTML_CONVERSION=1
        UCONFIG_USE_WINDOWS_LCID_MAPPING_API=0
        U_CHARSET_IS_UTF8=1
        U_USING_ICU_NAMESPACE=0
        U_ENABLE_DYLOAD=0
        USE_CHROMIUM_ICU=1
        U_ENABLE_TRACING=1
        U_ENABLE_RESOURCE_TRACING=0
        U_STATIC_IMPLEMENTATION
        ICU_UTIL_DATA_IMPL=ICU_UTIL_DATA_FILE
        )

target_include_directories(icuuc_private PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/icu/source/common/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/icu/source/i18n/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET icuuc_private PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja icuuc_private
        )

        ${libvpx_arm64_headers_sources}
        )

        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        )

        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET libvpx_arm64_headers PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja libvpx_arm64_headers
        )

        )

        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        )

        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        )

        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja libvpx_arm64_highbd_headers
        )

        ${libvpx_arm_headers_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(libvpx_arm_headers PRIVATE
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        )

target_include_directories(libvpx_arm_headers PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET libvpx_arm_headers PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja libvpx_arm_headers
        )

        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        )

        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        )

        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja libvpx_arm_neon_cpu_detect_headers
        )

        ${libvpx_arm_neon_headers_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(libvpx_arm_neon_headers PRIVATE
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        )

target_include_directories(libvpx_arm_neon_headers PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET libvpx_arm_neon_headers PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja libvpx_arm_neon_headers
        )

        ${libvpx_arm_neon_highbd_headers_sources}
        )

        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        )

        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        )

        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja libvpx_arm_neon_highbd_headers
        )

        ${libvpx_generic_headers_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(libvpx_generic_headers PRIVATE
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        )

target_include_directories(libvpx_generic_headers PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET libvpx_generic_headers PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja libvpx_generic_headers
        )

        ${libvpx_x86_64_headers_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(libvpx_x86_64_headers PRIVATE
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        )

target_include_directories(libvpx_x86_64_headers PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET libvpx_x86_64_headers PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja libvpx_x86_64_headers
        )


set(libvpx_x86_headers_sources
        ${EMPTY_PATH}

        ${libvpx_x86_headers_sources}
        )

target_compile_definitions(libvpx_x86_headers PRIVATE
        _GNU_SOURCE
        ANDROID
        HAVE_SYS_UIO_H
        ANDROID_NDK_VERSION_ROLL=r22_1
        __STDC_CONSTANT_MACROS
        __STDC_FORMAT_MACROS
        _DEBUG
        DYNAMIC_ANNOTATIONS_ENABLED=1
        )

target_include_directories(libvpx_x86_headers PRIVATE
        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        )

add_custom_command(TARGET libvpx_x86_headers PRE_BUILD
        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja libvpx_x86_headers
        )


set(libvpxrc_sources
        ${EMPTY_PATH}

        HAVE_PTHREAD
        )

        ${webrtc_source_path}
        ${webrtc_build_path}/gen/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/protobuf/src/
        ${webrtc_source_path}third_party/zlib/
        )

        WORKING_DIRECTORY ${webrtc_build_path}/
        COMMAND ninja protobuf_full
